    "title": "Schedule II",
    "html": "<p align=\"center\"><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\"><b>The Second Schedule<br>\n(See section 3)<br>\nAmendments</b></font></p>\n\n<table border=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"2\" width=\"100%\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\"><b>Year</b></font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\"><b>No.</b></font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\"><b>Short title</b></font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\"><b>Amendments</b></font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\">2013</font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\">25</font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\">The Prohibition of Employment as Manual Scavengers and their Rehabilitation Act, 2013</font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\">In the proviso to sub-section (3) of section 1, for the words \"the notification\", the words \"the said notification\" shall be substituted.</font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\">2014</font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\">17</font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\">The Whistle Blowers Protection Act, 2011</font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\">(a) In the Enacting Formula, for the words \"Sixty-second Year\", the words \"Sixty-fifth Year\" shall be substituted; and</font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"3\"><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\"></font></td>\n      <td><font style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:12px\">(b) in sub-section (1) of section 1, for the figures \"2011\", the figures \"2014\" shall be substituted.</font></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<!-- END : Content Area -->\n\t\t\t\